Package windows.tableModels

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangeCardTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the users that are banned.
    HouseCharacteristicsTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the characteristics of a house.
    MyHousesTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the houses an specific user has created.
    MyOffersTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the offers from a specific user.
    OfferOpinionsTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the opinions of an offer.
    ReservationTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the offers that a user has booked.
    SearchResultTableModel
    Table model for the tables used to present the result of a search in the system.
